# 5. Legal Requirements & Compliance Checklist (Karnataka, India)

## Essential Registrations

### 1. FSSAI Registration/License

Mandatory for all food businesses in India, including home bakers and dessert brands. ([fssai.gov.in](https://www.fssai.gov.in/cms/registration.php?utm_source=chatgpt.com))

* Basic Registration: Small businesses/home kitchens
* State License: Medium-scale businesses
* Central License: Large multi-state businesses

Official Portal:
[FoSCoS FSSAI Registration Portal](https://foscos.fssai.gov.in/apply-for-lic-and-reg?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

### 2. GST Registration

Required if turnover crosses the legal threshold or if selling through marketplaces/platforms.

### 3. Trade License / Shop & Establishment Registration

May be required by your local municipal authority.

### 4. Trademark Registration

Recommended to protect your brand name/logo.

### 5. Business Entity Registration

Optional initially but recommended:

* Sole Proprietorship
* Partnership
* LLP
* Private Limited Company

---

