## Important Notes

* FSSAI registration is mandatory even for small home-based food businesses. ([timesofindia.indiatimes.com](https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bengaluru/registration-with-fssai-must-for-small-home-food-businesses/articleshow/79116828.cms?utm_source=chatgpt.com))
* Home bakers and online dessert sellers are required to comply with food safety rules. ([cleartax.in](https://cleartax.in/s/home-bakers-fssai-registration?utm_source=chatgpt.com))
* Food businesses must display their FSSAI registration/license number on packaging. ([cleartax.in](https://cleartax.in/s/fssai-registration?utm_source=chatgpt.com))

